<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285166>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Map with the points of occurrence of the species of Termitomorpha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285166/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285113>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A) Head, dorsal view. B) Left and right mandibles, dorsal view. C) Pronotum, dorsal view. D) Prosternum, ventral view. E) Antenna. F) Mentum and labium, ventral view. G) Labrum, ventral view. H) Maxilla, dorsal view. Scales bars: A, B, D, F, G = 0,15 mm; C, E, H = 0,3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285123>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A) Elytron, ventral view. B) Detail of the anteromesial border of elytron, internal view. C) Mandible, dorsal view. D) Subapical tooth of mandible, dorsal view. E) Maxilla; F) Maxillary palpus. Scales bars: A = 200 µm; B, D = 20 µm; C, F = 50 µm; E = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285115>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A) Meso-metaventrite, ventral view. B) Meso-metanotum and tergite I, dorsal view. C) Elytron, dorsal view. D) Front leg. E) Female middle leg (arrow showing ventral surface of anterior region with notch). F) Male middle leg, male (arrow showing ventral surface of anterior region without notch). G) Hind leg. Scales bars: A–C = 0,15 mm; D–G = 0,3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285115/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285119>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A) Tergite II, dorsal view. B) Tergite VII, dorsal view. C) Tergite VIII, dorsal view. D) Female sternite VIII, dorsal view. E) Female tergites IX and X, dorsal view. F) Male sternite VIII, dorsal view. G) Male tergites IX and X, dorsal view. H) Aedeagus, paramere, lateral view. I) Aedeagus, median lobe, lateral view. J) Male sternite IX, lateral view. K) Spermatheca. Scales bars: A–I = 0,3 mm; J = 0,15 mm; K = 0,7 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285125>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A) Tergite VII, dorsal view. B–C) Gland opening of tergite VII, dorsal view. Scales bars: A = 200 µm; B = 50 µm; C = 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285159>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. A–B) Nest of Nasutitermes corniger (Moschulsky) where the type material of Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. was found." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285135>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Termitomorpha goeldiana sp. nov. A–C) Living specimen interacting with termites Nasutitermis corniger (Moschulsky)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

